descriptionHtml:
♬♪ Content List ♪♬

1.Umbrella
Night of pouring rain. Under an abandoned umbrella, Red eating sausages alone between rava and her friends who are hungry! I got you! Give me
2.Cheese
Hungry Red, Yellow and Brown. No, let's take the cheese while she's asleep! While yum yum yum yum yum eating cheese, the mouse woke up?! Larva and friends wandering between cheese and rats!
3.Distress 1
Cold winter days with heavy snow. Red and Yellow, who were always running away from mice today, barely escaped with their pouting bricks, but my goodness! We can't go back, can we?!
4.Distress 2
Never fall asleep! Red and yellow wake me up with all their might just in case my friend falls asleep. But you're really trying to wake me up for my friend, right?

▶ Popular anime LARVA Season content video at once!

You can meet various Larva Season content videos full of personality!

▶ Simple and easy to use interface

Just launch the app and the content video will automatically play without complicated buttons, Larva Season content videos without complicated buttons.
You can enjoy a variety of content for free just by watching the ads ~!

▶ Caution
All videos can be watched for free, but data charges may occur, so we recommend using them in unlimited plans or in WIFI environments.

▶ Guide by Access Rights
When using the game, we request access to provide the following services.
